Package ohos.interwork.bundle

Class ElementNameEx

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.interwork.bundle.ElementNameEx
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParcelableEx, Sequenceable

    public class ElementNameEx
extends Object
implements Sequenceable, ParcelableEx
    Contains basic Ability information, which uniquely identifies an ability. In a HarmonyOS process, your ability basic information is stored in a ElementNameEx object. This object will be marshalled and then transmitted to a process in another platform. After receiving the marshalled object, that process will unmarshal it and then read the data.
    Since:
    3
